            "text": "<p>The Boring Foods Company is operated by Agsto Foods Private Limited, an FSSAI-licensed food business based in Gurugram, India. All our products are manufactured, stored, and distributed in accordance with applicable food safety regulations.</p><p><em>Our products are food items intended for general wellness and nutrition. They are not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease.</em></p>",
